snippet.title: Tomb Raider 3 Walkthrough - Temple Ruins (Level 2)
snippet.description:
Welcome to a walkthrough of Tomb Raider 3 with all secret locations revealed. Tomb Raider 3 was developed by Core Design and released in 1998. Lara must go in search of pieces of a meteorite that have been scattered around the world. Unlike past Tomb Raider games you'll be able to decide what locations to travel to next. It features better graphics, more abilities and vehicles.

Walkthrough: http://gamerwalkthroughs.com/tomb-raider-3/
